leaf
====

Leaf is a training project made in c++, the purpose of leaf is a simple web server to upload files and download them later.
A demo version of leaf is available at leaf.fleur.is

Known issues
------------

- File integrity change due to multipart text at the end of the file,
  it can be see when opening text file at the end, for images, pdf, zip, bin, etc the hash change.


Todo
----

[ ] File size limit
