Prerequisites
-------------

- C++ compiler
- cmake

Dependencies
------------

- libcex
  - libevhtp


How to use
----------

1. clone the repo
2. install libcex Dependencies (libevhtp)
    can be installed with package manager
3. cd leaf
4. chmod +x configure.sh
5. run ./configure.sh to run cmake
6. chmod +x build.sh
7. run ./build.sh
8. leaf app is under out/buil/leaf*

Contribution
------------

Feel free to open an issue to report a bug or any suggestions.
